## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="43193-102">Nell'esempio seguente fa parte del file code-behind per il modello di pagina di INSERT.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43193-102">The following example is part of the code-behind file for the Insert.aspx page template.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43193-103">Il <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaTable> viene inizializzata nell'istanza di `Page_Load` (metodo).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43193-103">The <xref:System.Web.DynamicData.MetaTable> instance is initialized in the `Page_Load` method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="43193-104">Il titolo della pagina è impostato su tabella `DisplayName` proprietà.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43193-104">The title for the page is set to the table `DisplayName` property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public partial class Insert : System.Web.UI.Page {  
    protected MetaTable table;     
  
    protected void Page_Load(object sender, EventArgs e) {  
        table = DetailsDataSource.GetTable();  
        Title = table.DisplayName;  
    }  
}  
```  
  
```vb  
Partial Class Insert  
    Inherits System.Web.UI.Page  
  
    Protected table As MetaTable      
  
    Protected Sub Page_Load(ByVal sender As Object, _  
            ByVal e As EventArgs)  
        table = DetailsDataSource.GetTable  
        Title = table.DisplayName  
    End Sub  
End Class  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="43193-243">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come creare un dizionario di chiave primaria.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="43193-243">The following example shows how to create a primary-key dictionary.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private RouteValueDictionary GetRouteValues(MetaTable table, object row) {  
    RouteValueDictionary routeValues = GetRouteValues();  
    foreach (var pk in table.GetPrimaryKeyDictionary(row)) {  
        routeValues[pk.Key] = pk.Value;  
    }  
    return routeValues;  
}   
```  
  
```vb  
Private Function GetRouteValues(ByVal table As MetaTable, _  
        ByVal row As Object) As RouteValueDictionary   
    Dim routeValues As RouteValueDictionary = GetRouteValues()   
    For Each pk In table.GetPrimaryKeyDictionary(row)   
        routeValues(pk.Key) = pk.Value   
    Next   
    Return routeValues   
End Function   
```
